She looked at him. "Yes Quickstrike." She saw he was getting 
aggitated with her.  She tried to stand so  she could talk to him 
outside that lab, she thought, that way he might talk to her a little 
easier.  besides, the lab was making her uncomfortable as well.  She 
slid off the table side and landed on her feet.  She stood there for 
about half a second then fell to the floor.
